    <h2>About Hostels</h2>
    <p>LBS College of Engineering Kasaragod (LBSCEK) offers accommodation for students opting for Hostel Admission. There are three in-campus and three out-campus hostels providing fully furnished facilities for boys and girls separately. Hostels are managed by the Hostel Warden, assisted by Resident Tutors, H’RTs, and Matrons.</p>
    <p>Facilities include 24x7 Wi-Fi, indoor games, knowledge sharing, mutual care, and a dedicated mess with quality food. Guest rooms are also available.</p>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:warden@lbscek.ac.in">warden@lbscek.ac.in</a></p>
