<div class="section">
    <h2>Hostel Rules & Guidelines</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Allotment is only for students/staff of the institute.</li>
        <li>Priority based on distance from hometown.</li>
        <li>No students with unsatisfactory background (e.g., criminal cases) admitted.</li>
        <li>Room allotment by Resident Tutor/Warden.</li>
        <li>Minimum period of stay: 1 year.</li>
        <li>Vacating early: pay establishment charges; completion: exempted.</li>
        <li>Room changes require permission.</li>
        <li>Inmates responsible for hostel property.</li>
        <li>Damage to property is punished.</li>
        <li>Undertaking required at admission.</li>
        <li>Ragging strictly banned.</li>
        <li>Prohibited: electric cookers, high volume speakers.</li>
        <li>Clear dues before shifting hostels.</li>
        <li>Contagious disease: not allowed.</li>
        <li>No outsiders without permission.</li>
        <li>Lock doors/cupboards before leaving.</li>
        <li>Switch off lights/fans before leaving room.</li>
        <li>No wall defacement.</li>
        <li>Alcohol/narcotics prohibited.</li>
        <li>No unauthorized meetings/events.</li>
        <li>No furniture shifting without permission.</li>
        <li>No weapons or metals stored.</li>
        <li>Hostel inspection allowed anytime.</li>
        <li>No removal of common newspapers/magazines.</li>
        <li>Half rent charged for half-month stay.</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>Mess, Hygiene & Discipline</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Monthly mess committee elected.</li>
        <li>Committee responsible for hygiene, food quality.</li>
        <li>Menu published in advance.</li>
        <li>Mess cut applications 1 day before.</li>
        <li>Mess secretary elected.</li>
        <li>Guests can pay for food.</li>
        <li>Max 15 mess cuts per month.</li>
        <li>Minimum 5 consecutive days for cut.</li>
        <li>Extra food available for extra payment.</li>
        <li>Mess bill fine policy.</li>
        <li>Visitors register maintained.</li>
        <li>Late-night movement logged.</li>
        <li>ID card produced on request.</li>
        <li>Men’s hostel closes 9:00 p.m. (MH1-3), 8:00 p.m. (MH4).</li>
        <li>Ladies hostel closes 6:00 p.m.</li>
        <li>Violation invites punitive action.</li>
        <li>Rules amended by authorities as needed.</li>
    </ol>
